WEBVTT

00:00:00.583 --> 00:00:03.059
Chris Anderson: Welcome to TED Connects.

00:00:03.083 --> 00:00:09.643
This is a new series
of live conversations,

00:00:09.667 --> 00:00:13.351
trying to make sense
of this weird moment that we're in:

00:00:13.375 --> 00:00:14.976
coronavirus.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:18.393
Everyone's suddenly changing
how they live their lives,

00:00:18.417 --> 00:00:21.809
it's so jolting, it's so startling.

00:00:21.833 --> 00:00:25.476
We're all trying to make sense of it,
and it ain't easy.

00:00:25.500 --> 00:00:26.809
That much we know.

00:00:26.833 --> 00:00:29.184
We're trying to make sense
of this together

00:00:29.208 --> 00:00:30.851
in the only way that we know how,